"    portability of scripts across the different platforms.  These codes "
"include:\n"
"    remove zero-padding (e.g. `%-d` and `%-m` on Linux or macOS, and their\n"
"    equivalent `%#d` and `%#m` on Windows); element length specifiers (e.g.\n"
